cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.GT, cs.MM

This paper deals with optimizing energy efficiency in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network optimization and communication theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves mathematical formulations and analysis, indicating a possible fit for cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The problem of cluster formation and activation time setting can be viewed as a game-theoretic problem, which suggests a possible fit for cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Finally, the paper involves numerical simulations, which could be related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
